      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M-differential lock. Recent mechanical updates include a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a VANOS bulletproofing kit, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension maintains factory-spec damping with refreshed polyurethane bushings, preserving the chassis's renowned communicative feedback and turn-in precision. The exterior retains its original aerodynamic profile with minor patina consistent with enthusiast use, while the interior remains a focused environment with operational lateral support bolsters.",
